text: Lago del Narèt is a lake in Val Sambuco, Ticino, Switzerland. Its surface area is . It is located in the municipality of Lavizzara. The closest village is Fusio. ==See also== *List of lakes of Switzerland *List of mountain lakes of Switzerland ==External links== *Laghetti alpini della Svizzera italiana: Attorno al Naret Category:Lakes of Ticino Category:Reservoirs in Switzerland
